      <h3>The Castello delle Serre</h3>
      <p>The venue for the wedding reception, the <a href="https://castellodelleserre.com/" target="_blank">Castello dello Serre</a>, provides fantastic, luxury accommodation with stunning views across the Tuscan hills.</p>
      <p>There are 20 double rooms in the Castello, many of which have the facility for extra single or double beds to be added.  We can offer these for £100 per room per night to any guests staying both Friday and Saturday nights, and an extra £30 per night for additional guests in the larger rooms.</p>
      <p>As well as superb rooms and a fabulous breakfast service, the roof-top pool will provide the ideal way to kill time before leaving for the wedding at 3pm, all with the convenience of having a short stagger back to your room once it's all over.  Please use the RSVP form to let us know if you're interested.</p>

